column5: Just looking for information on any road construction on Hwy 11 west of Fort Francis and North on Hwy 71 to Kenora. If any is there gravel ? Thanks
I ran thru there yesterday,Sunday, and didn't have any issues. Went only as far as 10 miles past Sioux Narrows.
Was though there 1st week of July. No gravel. Good roads all the way.
Thank You guys I can't wait..
